name: Lana Dobreed
Lore: 'Dobreed used to have dreams of opening up his own shop in Mos Espa. Now broke from his gambling activities, he provides transportation services to pay for his urges.',
Text: 'During your move phase, target any or all of your characters at one exterior site to ''transport'' (relocate) to another exterior site. Draw destiny. Use that much Force to ''transport,'' or place Interrupt in Lost Pile.',
